ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果時仲話要買咩錄影機同卡式錄音帶<br />\n宜家反而變返最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ef939a7768130bd060a713dd1d6663618e0e94","tid":1096653,"uid":64694,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:53:16.000Z","msg":"當個個都用電子產品，真人接觸變成奢侈品<br />\n之後啲人意識到呢點，之後變得更多真人接觸，電子產品又會變成奢侈品<br />\n之後啲人意識到電子產品變成奢侈品，真人接觸又變成奢侈品<br />\n之後不停loop落去，所謂嘅週期性就係咁，一個循環不息嘅cycle，因為物極會必反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3715a6e3a54321baf47d870ab4f595dc1bdbc5a","tid":1096653,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當個個都用電子產品，真人接觸變成奢侈品<br />\n之後啲人意識到呢點，之後變得更多真人接觸，電子產品又會變成奢侈品<br />\n之後啲人意識到電子產品變成奢侈品，<span style=\"color: red;\">之後又多咗人用電子產品</span>，真人接觸又變成奢侈品<br />\n之後不停loop落去，所謂嘅週期性就係咁，一個循環不息嘅cycle，因為物極會必反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"af4eaa14f6fcf481ad93e5e132c323440b7cd9e1","tid":1096653,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"804cdc298b114bb8fb44f127502e9ec538e6d285","tid":1096653,"uid":55913,"like":169,"dislike":31,"score":138,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T00:52:42.000Z","msg":"總之做眾人皆醉撚攞優越感就最叻叻啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">富人＝連登仔</span></strong></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6179e6fedccab2996296b31e02d127a2ab56dc59","tid":1096653,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T18:26:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4763238cdd261f4fd690cedaf1749abe1e3e7e2","tid